#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:1.1.0"
msgid "77. Sañciccasikkhāpada"
msgstr ""
"<hgroup><h1 id=\"Bu-Pc.77\">Monks’ Confession 77: the training rule on "
"intentionally</h1></hgroup>"

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1, pts-vp-pli4.149
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:1.1.1"
msgid ""
"Tena samayena buddho bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa "
"ārāme."
msgstr ""
"<h2 id=\"nidana\">Origin story</h2><p><a class=\"pts-cs\" id=\"Bu-Pc.77.1\""
">Bu-Pc.77.1</a><a class=\"pts-vp-en\" id=\"BD.3.53\">BD.3.53</a><a class"
"=\"wt-pa\">1379</a>At one time the Buddha was staying at Sāvatthī in the "
"Jeta Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s Monastery."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:1.1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena chabbaggiyā bhikkhū sattarasavaggiyānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ "
"sañcicca kukkuccaṃ upadahanti—"
msgstr ""
"At that time the monks from the group of six intentionally made the monks "
"from the group of seventeen anxious, saying,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:1.1.3"
msgid "“bhagavatā, āvuso, sikkhāpadaṃ paññattaṃ—"
msgstr "“The Master has laid down a rule"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:1.1.4"
msgid "‘na ūnavīsativasso puggalo upasampādetabbo’ti."
msgstr ""
"that a person who is less than twenty years old shouldn’t be given the full "
"ordination."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:1.1.5"
msgid "Tumhe ca ūnavīsativassā upasampannā."
msgstr "And you were less than twenty when you got the full ordination."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:1.1.6"
msgid "Kacci no tumhe anupasampannā”ti?"
msgstr "Could it be that you are not fully ordained?”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:1.1.7"
msgid "Te rodanti."
msgstr "They cried."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:1.1.8"
msgid "Bhikkhū evamāhaṃsu—"
msgstr "Other monks asked them why,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:1.1.9"
msgid "“kissa tumhe, āvuso, rodathā”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:1.1.10"
msgid ""
"“Ime, āvuso, chabbaggiyā bhikkhū amhākaṃ sañcicca kukkuccaṃ upadahantī”ti."
msgstr ""
"and they said, “These monks from the group of six intentionally make us "
"anxious.”</p>"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:1.1.11"
msgid "Ye te bhikkhū appicchā … pe …"
msgstr ""
"<p><a class=\"pts-vp-pi\" id=\"Vin.4.149\">Vin.4.149</a><a class=\"wt-pa\""
">1380</a>The monks of few desires …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:1.1.12"
msgid "te ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "complained and criticized them,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:1.1.13"
msgid ""
"“kathañhi nāma chabbaggiyā bhikkhū bhikkhūnaṃ sañcicca kukkuccaṃ "
"upadahissantī”ti … pe …"
msgstr ""
"“How can the monks from the group of six intentionally make other monks "
"anxious?” …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:1.1.14"
msgid ""
"“saccaṃ kira tumhe, bhikkhave, bhikkhūnaṃ sañcicca kukkuccaṃ upadahathā”ti?"
msgstr "“Is it true, monks, that you do this?”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:1.1.15"
msgid "“Saccaṃ, bhagavā”ti."
msgstr "“It’s true, Master.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:1.1.16"
msgid "Vigarahi buddho bhagavā … pe …"
msgstr "The Buddha rebuked them, “…"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:1.1.17"
msgid ""
"kathañhi nāma tumhe, moghapurisā, bhikkhūnaṃ sañcicca kukkuccaṃ "
"upadahissatha."
msgstr "Foolish men, how can you intentionally make other monks anxious?"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:1.1.18"
msgid "Netaṃ, moghapurisā, appasannānaṃ vā pasādāya … pe …"
msgstr "This will not give rise to confidence in those without it …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:1.1.19"
msgid "evañca pana, bhikkhave, imaṃ sikkhāpadaṃ uddiseyyātha—"
msgstr "And, monks, this training rule should be recited thus:</p>"

#. HTML: </p><p><b class="rule">
#. REF: sc3
#. VAR: upadaheyya → uppādeyya (itipi)
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:1.1.20"
msgid ""
"“Yo pana bhikkhu bhikkhussa sañcicca kukkuccaṃ upadaheyya—‘itissa muhuttampi "
"aphāsu bhavissatī’ti etadeva paccayaṃ karitvā anaññaṃ, pācittiyan”ti."
msgstr ""
"<h2 id=\"pannatti\">Final ruling</h2><p class=\"rule\"><a class=\"wt-pa\""
">1381</a>‘If a monk intentionally makes another monk anxious, thinking, “In "
"this way he will be ill at ease at least for a moment,” and he does so only "
"for this reason and no other, he commits an offense entailing "
"confession.’”</p>"

#. HTML: </b></p><p><b class="term">
#. REF: sc4
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:2.1.1"
msgid "Yo panāti"
msgstr ""
"<h2 id=\"pada\">Definitions</h2><p><a class=\"pts-cs\" id=\"Bu-Pc.77.2\""
"></a><a class=\"pts-cs\" id=\"Bu-Pc.77.2.1\">Bu-Pc.77.2.1</a><a class=\"wt-"
"pa\">1382</a><term>A</term>:"

#. HTML: </b><b class="gloss">
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:2.1.2"
msgid "yo yādiso … pe …"
msgstr "<gloss>whoever …</gloss>"

#. HTML: </b><b class="term">
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:2.1.3"
msgid "bhikkhūti"
msgstr "<term>Monk</term>:"

#. HTML: </b><b class="gloss">
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:2.1.4"
msgid "… pe …"
msgstr "<gloss>…"

#. HTML: </b>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:2.1.5"
msgid "ayaṃ imasmiṃ atthe adhippeto bhikkhūti."
msgstr ""
"The monk who has been given the full ordination by a complete Order through "
"a procedure consisting of one motion and three announcements that is "
"unchallengeable and fit to stand—this sort of monk is meant in this "
"case.</gloss></p>"

#. HTML: </p><p><b class="term">
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:2.1.6"
msgid "Bhikkhussāti"
msgstr ""
"<p><a class=\"pts-vp-en\" id=\"BD.3.54\">BD.3.54</a><a class=\"wt-pa\""
">1383</a><term>Another monk</term>:"

#. HTML: </b><b class="gloss">
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:2.1.7"
msgid "aññassa bhikkhussa."
msgstr "<gloss>a different monk.</gloss></p>"

#. HTML: </b></p><p><b class="term">
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:2.1.8"
msgid "Sañciccāti"
msgstr "<p><a class=\"wt-pa\">1384</a><term>Intentionally</term>:"

#. HTML: </b><b class="gloss">
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:2.1.9"
msgid "jānanto sañjānanto cecca abhivitaritvā vītikkamo."
msgstr ""
"<gloss>knowing, perceiving, having intended, having decided, he "
"transgresses.</gloss></p>"

#. HTML: </b></p><p><b class="term">
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:2.1.10"
msgid "Kukkuccaṃ upadaheyyāti"
msgstr "<p><a class=\"wt-pa\">1385</a><term>Makes […] anxious</term>:"

#. HTML: </b><b class="gloss">
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:2.1.11"
msgid ""
"“ūnavīsativasso maññe tvaṃ upasampanno, vikāle maññe tayā bhuttaṃ, majjaṃ "
"maññe tayā pītaṃ, mātugāmena saddhiṃ raho maññe tayā nisinnan”ti kukkuccaṃ "
"upadahati, āpatti pācittiyassa."
msgstr ""
"<gloss>if he makes him anxious, saying, “It would seem that you were less "
"than twenty years old when you were given the full ordination/it would seem "
"that you have eaten at the wrong time/it would seem that you have drunk "
"alcohol/it would seem that you have been sitting in private with a woman,” "
"he commits an offense entailing confession.</gloss></p>"

#. HTML: </b></p><p><b class="term">
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:2.1.12"
msgid "Etadeva paccayaṃ karitvā, anaññanti"
msgstr ""
"<p><a class=\"wt-pa\">1386</a><term>He does so only for this reason and no "
"other</term>:"

#. HTML: </b><b class="gloss">
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:2.1.13"
msgid "na añño koci paccayo hoti kukkuccaṃ upadahituṃ."
msgstr "<gloss>there is no other reason for making him anxious.</gloss></p>"

#. HTML: </b></p><p>
#. REF: sc9
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:2.2.1"
msgid ""
"Upasampanne upasampannasaññī sañcicca kukkuccaṃ upadahati, āpatti "
"pācittiyassa."
msgstr ""
"<h2 id=\"cakka\">Permutations</h2><p><a class=\"pts-cs\" id=\"Bu-Pc.77.2.2\""
">Bu-Pc.77.2.2</a><a class=\"wt-pa\">1387</a>If it is one who is fully "
"ordained, and he perceives him as fully ordained, and he intentionally makes "
"him anxious, he commits an offense entailing confession."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:2.2.2"
msgid "Upasampanne vematiko sañcicca kukkuccaṃ upadahati, āpatti pācittiyassa."
msgstr ""
"If it is one who is fully ordained, but he is unsure if he is, and he "
"intentionally makes him anxious, he commits an offense entailing confession."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:2.2.3"
msgid ""
"Upasampanne anupasampannasaññī sañcicca kukkuccaṃ upadahati, āpatti "
"pācittiyassa."
msgstr ""
"If it is one who is fully ordained, but he does not perceive him as fully "
"ordained, and he intentionally makes him anxious, he commits an offense "
"entailing confession.</p>"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:2.2.4"
msgid "Anupasampannassa sañcicca kukkuccaṃ upadahati, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"<p><a class=\"wt-pa\">1388</a>If he intentionally makes one who is not fully "
"ordained anxious, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:2.2.5"
msgid "Anupasampanne upasampannasaññī, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"If it is one who is not fully ordained, but he perceives him as fully "
"ordained, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:2.2.6"
msgid "Anupasampanne vematiko, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"If it is one who is not fully ordained, but he is unsure of it, he commits "
"an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:2.2.7"
msgid "Anupasampanne anupasampannasaññī, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"If it is one who is not fully ordained, and he does not perceive him as "
"fully ordained, he commits an offense of wrong conduct.</p>"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:2.3.1"
msgid "Anāpatti—"
msgstr ""
"<h2 id=\"anapatti\">Non-offenses</h2><p><a class=\"pts-cs\" id=\"Bu-Pc.77.2."
"3\">Bu-Pc.77.2.3</a><a class=\"wt-pa\">1389</a>There is no offense:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:2.3.2"
msgid ""
"na kukkuccaṃ upadahitukāmo “ūnavīsativasso maññe tvaṃ upasampanno, vikāle "
"maññe tayā bhuttaṃ, majjaṃ maññe tayā pītaṃ, mātugāmena saddhiṃ raho maññe "
"tayā nisinnaṃ, iṅgha jānāhi, mā te pacchā kukkuccaṃ ahosī”ti bhaṇati, "
"ummattakassa, ādikammikassāti."
msgstr ""
"if, not wanting to make him anxious, he says, “It would seem that you were "
"less than twenty years old when you were given the full ordination/it would "
"seem that you have eaten at the wrong time/it would seem that you have drunk "
"alcohol/it would seem that you have been sitting in private with a woman—"
"find out about it, so that you don’t get anxious later;” if he is insane; if "
"he is the first offender.</p>"

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsutta">
#. REF: sc12
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc77:2.3.3"
msgid "Sañciccasikkhāpadaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
"<hr><p class=\"endsutta\"><a class=\"wt-pa\">1390</a>The seventh rule, the "
"training rule on intentionally, is finished.</p>"
